title: the newspaper of your birth
description:
the newspaper of your birth:

Seize a name and a birth date: A page ready to be printed is then posted comprising the current events of your year of birth, the celebrities born the same day (actors, sportsmen, artists, musicians), your astrological profile (sign of the zodiac and Chinese astrology), the events of year (famous films, inventions, Goncourt prices, Nobel Prize, songs, etc), a heading sport with the most outstanding scores (football, cycling, Rugby, automobile race, tennis, etc) and your stone of birthday! The result is entirely modifiable thanks to the integrated editor. The database goes from 1900 to 2002. An ideal gift for the festivals and birthdays!
